bar.plugin
Class Commander

java.lang.Object
  bar.plugin.Commander
All Implemented Interfaces:
PlugIn, ActionListener, KeyListener, MouseListener, WindowListener, EventListener, DocumentListener, ListSelectionListener
public class Commander
extends Object
implements PlugIn, ActionListener, DocumentListener, KeyListener, ListSelectionListener, MouseListener, WindowListener

Implements a light-weight and fast keyboard-based file browser for ImageJ (BAR>BAR Commander... command). . A summary of features is listed on the BAR documentation page.

Commander is modeled after CommandFinder by Mark Longair and FunctionFinder by Jerome Mutterer. It is also influenced by Johannes Schindelin's Recent_Commands plugin and a bit of DOS nostalgia. Drag and drop support is implemented by FileDrop (website).
